fields.introduction:
Dear Red Tide Swimmer,

As our team continues to grow, we on the Board of Directors want to make sure Red Tide swimmers have the best swimming experience possible.To learn more about you and your interests, and to help us seek team sponsors, supporters and new members, we ask that you take a few minutes to take the Red Tide Survey. Please complete the survey by 5:00 p.m. on August 15.


The survey was put together by the Board of Directors and team members Eldar Beiseitov and Emre Aydin; Fred Grim provided technical support. Please be assured that your responses are confidential and for team use only. If you have any questions or thoughts, contact survey@redtidenyc.org.

Thank you for your participation,

Red Tide Board of Directors

If RT is not friendly to triathletes training all freestyle, please make this public. I felt attacked by Tyrone's behavoir during the practice. The benefit I gain from swimming other strokes is minial and I don't anticipate learning the other strokes.
